            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/bad-end-theater-coming-to-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-xbox-one-and-switch-on-july-10<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Serenity Forge [66 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/serenity-forge">Serenity Forge</a> and developer <a title="Companies > NomnomNami" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nomnomnami">NomnomNami</a> will release <a title="Genres > Visual Novel [574 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/visual-novel">visual novel</a> <em><a title="Games > BAD END THEATER" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/bad-end-theater">BAD END THEATER</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,759 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,433 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,100 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,033 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, and <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,248 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a> on July 10, the companies <a href="https://serenityforge.com/games/bad-end-theater/" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-974731"></span></p><p><em>BAD END THEATER</em> first launched for PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1764390/BAD_END_THEATER/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on October 26, 2021.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via Serenity Forge:</p><blockquote><p>Welcome to <em>BAD END THEATER</em>!</p><p>Select your protagonist and explore a variety of terrible fates!</p><p>The decisions you make in one story will affect the others. You can toggle these behaviors to open up new paths! Unfortunately, every path leads to a bad endingâ€¦</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Can you find a way to save this unlucky cast?</p></blockquote><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>Consoles Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="BAD END THEATER - Console Announcement Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YR2ZSly6lwM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
